Interface SimulatorInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
CarWashSimulator
public interface SimulatorInterface
Interface for a car wash simulator.

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type Method Description
    double getAverageWaitTime()
    After this simulation is complete, returns the average time cars had to wait.
    int getCarsWithZeroWait()
    After this simulation is complete, returns the number of cars that didn't have to wait at all before being washed.
    java.lang.String getLog()
    returns a minute by minute log as well as a summary of the most recent simulation.
    int getMaxWaitTime()
    After this simulation is complete, returns the number maximum time a car had to wait.
    int getNumberOfCarsWashed()
    After this simulation is complete, returns the number of cars washed.
    int getSimulatedMinutes()
    After this simulation is complete, returns the number of simulated minutes.
    void runSimulation()
    Starts this simulation using a random number generator seeded with the default seed.

    Starts this simulation using a random number generator seeded with the given parameter.
